## Development

To install all the dependencies

```
poetry install --with dev
```

Install the pre-commit hooks
    
```
pre-commit install
```
    
To test

```
poetry run pytest
```

Bump the version to publish
    
```
poetry version patch
git add fao56_model
git commit -am 'Bump version'
git push
```

